com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport
Class Entity

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.CoreItem
      com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.Item
          com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.Entity

public final class Entity
extends Item

A kind of Item that represents a real-world object.

Any Entity in the Analysis Repository can also be the owner of a set, which is a logical grouping of Items that might be used for multiple purposes.

An entity that owns a set holds references to the versions of the Entitys and Links it contains. If a contained Item is changed or deleted outside the set, then the set remains unaffected.

Entitys do not provide direct access to any set that they own. Set manipulation functionality is available through the command service and the item retrieval service.

Since:
1.0
